'''TEDxYouth@Doha''' is an independently organized [[TED conference]] which is localized to the youth in [[Qatar]]. The event is held annually in the month of November to commemorate [[United Nations]] [[Universal Children's Day]]. Youngsters across the nation aging from 15 - 18 are recruited as speakers in the event. The theme of this event is #failbetter. The inaugural TEDxYouthDay event took place on November 19, 2011 in Doha, Qatar to celebrate UN Universal Children's Day.

The second annual edition was held on November 17, 2012.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ictqatar.qa/en/news-events/news/celebrating-power-youth|title=Celebrating the Power of Youth|publisher=Ministry of Information and Communications Technology (Qatar)|date=16 December 2012|accessdate=2 December 2015}}</ref>

